item.content:encoded:
A week long Inter Institutional Cricket Tournament for boys and throw ball tournament for girls are being organized in RRMCH as a part of celebration of the Chairman’s birthday which falls on the 25th of September


Professors of RRMCH and honorable dignitaries watch the participants in action competing for the of “Chairman’s Trophy” with a focused attention. This inter- institutional competition which includes cricket tournament for boys and throw ball competition for girls has been launched as a part of celebration of the chairman’s birthday.

The RRMCH cricket team poses before the camera at the onset of the Chairman’s Trophy on the eve of the Chairman’s birthday

RRMCH cricket team in action in the inter institutional cricket competition of Chairman’s Trophy 2012
